{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_08_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 このままじゃ出られません",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もう待ち合わせ時間はとっくに過ぎてるけど……\n愛はどうしたんだろう。今夜は行かないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s way past our meeting time…\nI wonder what happened to Ai. Isn’t she coming tonight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4325580907,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3000.7752426000006,
          "startTime": 7.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……遅くなってすみません、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry I’m late‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9133332569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.6566672483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "突然ごめんなさい\n今夜の食べ歩きは中止でお願いします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really sorry‚ but\nI have to cancel our ramen crawl tonight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　いや、俺は構わないけど……\n元気がないな。何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? No‚ I don’t mind…\nYou seem down. Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.420000553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、その、実は私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you see‚ actually…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.420000553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.9400018373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、やっぱり恥ずかしくて言えませんっ！\n{user}さんに呆れられちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu‚ it’s too embarrassing to say!\n{user}-san will be disappointed in me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は何があっても愛に呆れたりなんかしない\n安心してなんでも話してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t be disappointed in you no matter what happens‚ Ai.\nso please tell me everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 43.7899113654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　本当に呆れたりしませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? You really won’t be disappointed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7899113654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、マネージャーに二言はない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ a manager never goes back on his word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5717941761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 52.9147420265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。お話しします。あの……私……\n……らないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. I’ll tell you. You see… I…\n…don’t…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.2580684027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　ごめん、聞こえなかった。もう一度言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Sorry‚ I didn’t hear you. Please say it again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2580684027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 68.9497463228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だから……いらないんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-so… I don’t need it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9497463228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない、もう少し大きな声で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry‚ could you say that a little louder…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1348473392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 74.1348473392
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、だから私、ラーメンの食べ過ぎで\n太っちゃって衣装が入らないんですっっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu‚ so‚ you see‚ because I’ve been eating so much ramen‚\nI’ve gotten fat and my costumes don’t fit anymore!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃ、ライブに出られません！\nどうしましょうっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t go on stage like this!\nWhat should I do!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7446530685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいな……計算上、愛の運動量なら\nスタイルは維持出来るはずなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is strange… Based on my calculations‚ with how much exercise you’re getting‚ Ai‚\nyou should be able to maintain your figure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私も気にしてましたから\n毎日ちゃんと計算して、食べ歩きしていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ve been paying attention to that too‚\nso I’ve been carefully calculating everything and eating accordingly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.2427331769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "筋トレやランニングも多めにして\n普段の食事は少なめにしてましたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I increased the amount of muscle training and running I do‚\nand I’ve been eating less for my regular meals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日新衣装が届いたから着てみたんですけど\n腰のあたりがキツくて……踊ったら、破れちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But today‚ the new costume arrived and I tried it on‚\nand… it’s tight around my waist… It’ll rip if I dance in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8253607933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.515326389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな恥ずかしいことになったら\n莉央さんや葵さんにどんな顔をされるか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If such an embarrassing thing were to happen‚\nwhat face will I have to show Rio-san and Aoi-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1200008645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.8262374721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "こころには、一生ネタにされちゃいます！\nそうなったら、私、辞めるしかありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro will make fun of me for the rest of my life!\nIf that happens‚ I have no choice but to quit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て、芸能界引退なんて考えないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ don’t even think about retiring from the entertainment industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2957836312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.1009587449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、芸能界というか……\n日本で暮らすことをやめないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not the entertainment industry‚ but…\nI might have to stop living in Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8000066121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "誰も知らない土地にでも移住するつもりなのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re planning on moving to some place where no one knows you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6037176134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.9193636579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……どうしてこうなっちゃったんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu… how did it come to this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9193636579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、衣装をなんとかすることを考えよう\n今から頼んでサイズを直してもらえば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ let’s think about what to do about your costume.\nIf we ask now‚ they might be able to adjust the size…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4000066121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
